#SchemaDefinition -> Railt\SDL\Compiler\Ast\Definition\SchemaDefinitionNode:
    Documentation()?
    SchemaDefinitionHead()
    SchemaDefinitionBody()

SchemaDefinitionHead:
    ::T_SCHEMA:: TypeName()? Directives()?

SchemaDefinitionBody:
